HEADWORD: Tebeth
<hw>Te"beth</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Heb.]</ety> <def>The
tenth month of the Jewish ecclesiastical year, answering to a part of
December with a part of January.</def> <rj><au>Esther ii.
16.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
